      "note": "False positive (re-triaged CZID-48, 2026-06-17). download_file_with_retries fetches the S3 object to the fixed local dir /tmp/results_json and returns that local path; File.read reads the system-controlled local temp file, not a user-supplied path. The S3 key (s3_file_for) is derived server-side from the pipeline run, and the local filename uses the integer pipeline-run id, so no path traversal is possible."
