      "note": "Safe (re-triaged CZID-48, 2026-06-17). user_params (which permits :role) is only called by #create and #update, both gated by `before_action :admin_required` (they are not in the action's `except:` list). Non-admin self-service (#update_user_data) uses user_params_for_nonadmin, which does NOT permit :role. So :role cannot be mass-assigned by a non-admin."
